    <id>http://invalidusrname.github.com/blog/2012/03/10/meetup-events-in-octopress</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Have an Ocotpress-powered site and want to show upcoming meetup.com events? Check out <a href="https://github.com/invalidusrname/meetup-octopress">meetup-octopress</a>. It's a work in progress, but good enough to display dates and event names in the sidebar for the <a href="http://www.charlotteruby.org">Charlotte Ruby User Group</a>.</p>
